				<a  href="/article/2491360/solid-state-drives/sandisk-s-ultra-ii-ssd-offers-prices-as-low-as-44-cents-per-gigabyte.html">SanDisk&#039;s Ultra II SSD offers prices as low as 44 cents per gigabyte</a></h3>
				<h4>The Ultra II SSD is a follow-up to the consumer-grade Ultra Plus SSD released last year that increases performance while slashing the price point.</h4>
    		</div><!-- /.post-cont -->
		</div><!-- /.river-well -->
	







				
				
			
		
			
			
				
					
						
						
						
						
						
						
						
						
						
						
						
							
						
						
						
						
						
						
						
						
						 	
						
						
						
						
						
							
											
					
























	
	
		
		
	



	
	
